 - Removed last error gadget, now using requesters.

 @{u}@{fg shine}1.2 (22.4.97)@{uu}@{fg text}
  - Added my nick to the window title to indicate the I wrote it and not Ariel,
    so don't bother him with it.
  - Added Kuang11USR.guide (for this to work you'll need to install the
    new alias). Press the HELP key in the gui for online help.
  - Adding a user when 'No match <flags>' is shown in the listview now
    removes the 'No match' text (if the user flags match the one in the
    List by gadget of course).
  - Cleaned up the script again, gained some speed.
  - Now using rexxMOOS.library.
  - Added sorting of the listview by nicknames.

 @{u}@{fg shine}1.3 (??.??.??)@{uu}@{fg text}
  - Added some extra debug info.
