@node "Features" "Features       "

 @{u}@{fg shine}Kuang11USR features include@{uu}@{fg text}:

 · Easy interface for editing/adding/deleting users in the
   Kuang Eleven friends list.

 · Modification of all user flags as well as some preset settings.

 · Listing by flags (i.e. vop etc)

 · Adding/deleting hostnames to a user.
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements   "

 @{u}@{fg shine}Requirements@{uu}@{fg text}:

 Kuang Eleven 3.0 Gamma (19) or higher
 AmIRC 2.0 or higher
 MUIRexx 3.0 or higher
 rexxkuang11.library 0.19 or higher
 rexxtricks.library 38.6 or higher
 RexxRexTools.library (should at least be installed by Kuang Eleven)
@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction   "

 INTRODUCTION

    Kuang11USR was basically written because I wanted an easy
 way to modify the userlist in Kuang Eleven other than fooling
 around with the commandline args in AmIRC, hence Kuang11USR was
 created.

    This project took me roughly two weeks on and off to write.
 Anyway, here it is, have fun. Feedback and comments are always
 welcome. You can do so @{"here" link "Author" 0}.
@endnode

